        <updateDate>2007-12-14T14:30:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ Broadcast Ownership for the 21st Century Act - Directs the Federal Communications Commission (FCC) to modify current cross-ownership limitations by eliminating provisions limiting the granting or renewal of an AM or FM radio or television broadcast license to any party on the basis of the ownership, operation, or control of a daily newspaper. <p> <p> <p>]]></text>
      </summary>
